      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "ALL GOODNESS and truth are Yours, O God;\nmay no evil estrange us from You.\nLet error not confound us;\nhelp us understand Your will.\nIn adversity and prosperity, may Your law be our light.\nMay our deeds reflect Your love.\nבָּרוּךְ אַתָּה, יְיָ, אוֹהֵב עַמּוֹ יִשְׂרָאֵל.\nBaruch atah, Adonai, ohev amo Yisrael."
        }
      ],
